{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/affordance.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\">\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <title>Affordances</title>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;\n      charset=windows-1252\">\n  </head>\n  <body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n    <p><font size=\"7\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Affordances </font></p>\n    <p><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><i>\"term that\n          refers to the properties of objects -- what sorts of\n          operations and manipulations can be done to a particular\n          object\"</i> (D. A. Norman 1988, The Psychology of everyday\n        things). </font></p>\n    <ul>\n      <li><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">A door\n          affords opening</font></li>\n      <li><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">A chair\n          affords support</font></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">\"perceived\n        affordance\": the extent to which interface objects suggest their\n        affordance.<br>\n      </font></p>\n    <p><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">2nd revised\n        edition 2013: <b>Signifier</b><b>s</b> indicate the affordance\n        of an interface object. They need to be carefully designed to be\n        able to do this.<br>\n      </font></p>\n    <p><img src=\"affordances.jpg\" alt=\"The image shows the affordances\n        of door handles and scroll bars. The perceived performance of\n        some elements is better than that of other elements.\"\n        width=\"606\" height=\"285\"></p>\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\n    <table style=\"width: 817px; height: 124px;\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n      cellpadding=\"1\">\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td width=\"116\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img style=\"width: 97px; height:\n              69px;\" src=\"../../../graphics/pointing-finger-right.jpg\"></td>\n          <td width=\"587\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica,\n              sans-serif\">User interface elements should be designed in\n              such a way that they clearly indicate their affordances.</font><font\n              size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"> </font><a\n              href=\"lack-of-affordance.png\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,\n                Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 27px; height:\n                    34px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></font></font></a><font\n              size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"> </font><a\n              href=\"bad-affordance.png\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,\n                Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 27px; height:\n                    34px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></font></font></a><font\n              size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"> </font><font\n              size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><a\n                href=\"still-not-good-affordance.png\"><font size=\"6\"\n                  face=\"Wingdings\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ;\n                    width: 27px; height: 34px;\" alt=\"\"\n                    src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></font></a> </font><a\n              href=\"bad-affordance4.png\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,\n                Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 27px; height:\n                    34px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></font></font></a><font\n              size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"> </font><a\n              href=\"Misleading-perceived-affordance.png\"><font size=\"5\"\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\"\n                  face=\"Wingdings\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ;\n                    width: 27px; height: 34px;\" alt=\"\"\n                    src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"></font></font></a>\n            <a href=\"bad-affordance5.png\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,\n                Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 27px; height:\n                    34px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\">\n                </font></font></a><font size=\"6\"><font face=\"Wingdings\"></font></font><a\n              href=\"bad-signifier-bath1.jpg\"><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial,\n                Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\" face=\"Wingdings\"><img\n                    style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 27px; height:\n                    34px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\"\n                    width=\"27\" height=\"34\" border=\"0\"></font></font></a>\n            <a href=\"bad-signifier-bath2.jpg\"><font size=\"5\"\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font size=\"6\"\n                  face=\"Wingdings\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ;\n                    width: 27px; height: 34px;\" alt=\"\"\n                    src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down.gif\" width=\"27\"\n                    height=\"34\" border=\"0\"></font></font></a><br>\n            <br>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n    <p>&nbsp; <br>\n    </p>\n    <p><font size=\"5\" face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"></font></p>\n  </body>\n</html>\n", "encoding": "ascii"}